This is going to be a mail to bbs/blog that utilizes a few things.

The first is images to ascii, the second is a convoluted thread mechanic.

The third will be a bbs-type system that hosts both local and non local parts.

The serving of webpages will be handled by the gin/gonic engine and python
will handle the visual ncurses side of things

The mail server will be a secondary module of the golang area, as that's
what I'm trying to get back into the groove of

